## Setup Script Improvements

The `pi-setup.sh` script includes:
- Automatic unprivileged port configuration (Step 3b)
- Health check with retry logic: checks every 10s for up to 60s
- Separate container health checks and HTTP endpoint health checks
- Graceful failure with container logs on error
